Package jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.esx

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntityItemClassificationType
    The EntityItemClassificationType restricts a string value to a specific set of values that describe the classification of a given ESX Server patch.
    EntityItemSupportLevelType
    The EntityItemSupportLevelType restricts a string value to a specific set of values that describe the support level of a given ESX Server patch.
    EntityStateClassificationType
    The EntityStateClassificationType restricts a string value to a specific set of values that describe the classification of a given ESX Server patch.
    EntityStateSupportLevelType
    The EntityStateSupportLevelType restricts a string value to a specific set of values that describe the support level of a given ESX Server patch.
    Patch56Behaviors
    The Patch56Behaviors defines a number of behaviors that allow a more detailed definition of the patch56_object being specified.
    Patch56Object
    The patch56_object is used by a patch56_test to define those objects to be evaluated against a specified state.
    Patch56State
    The patch56_state defines the different information that can be used to evaluate the specified VMware ESX Serer patch.
    Patch56Test
    The patch56_test reveals the installation status of a specific patch or patches in VMware ESX Server.
    PatchBehaviors Deprecated
    Deprecated as of version 5.6: Replaced by the Patch56Behaviors and will be removed in a future version of the language.
    PatchItem
    Installation information about a specific patch in the VMware ESX server.
    PatchObject Deprecated
    Deprecated as of version 5.6: Replaced by the patch56 object and will be removed in a future version of the language.
    PatchState Deprecated
    Deprecated as of version 5.6: Replaced by the patch56 state and will be removed in a future version of the language.
    PatchTest Deprecated
    Deprecated as of version 5.6: Replaced by the patch56 test and will be removed in a future version of the language.
    VersionItem
    Information about the release and build version of VMware ESX server.
    VersionObject
    The version object is used by a version test to define those objects to be evaluated based on a specified state.
    VersionState
    The version state defines the information about the release and build version.
    VersionTest
    The version test reveals information about the release and build version of the VMware ESX server.
    ViSdkManagedEntityBehaviors
    The ViSdkManagedEntityBehaviors defines a number of behaviors that allow a more detailed definition of the visdkmanagedobject_object being specified.
    ViSdkManagedObjectItem
    The visdkmanagedobject item is used to represent information about Managed Objects in the VMware Infrastructure.
    ViSdkManagedObjectObject
    The visdkmanagedobject object is used by the visdkmanagedobject test to define those objects to be evaluated based on a specified state.
    ViSdkManagedObjectState
    The visdkmanagedobject state enumerates the different properties a Managed Entity might have.
    ViSdkManagedObjectTest
    The visdkmanagedobject test is used to check information about Managed Objects in the VMware Infrastructure.
